Spatial distribution of residential property prices in Hackney, 1995 - 2019

This map visualises the spatial distribution of Lower Layer Super Output Areas (LSOA) median price paid deciles for residential property sold between 1995 and 2019, for the local authority district of Hackney, London.

Data is sourced entirely from API data services, including the Ordnance Survey (OS) Data Hub, the HM Land Registry, and the Office for National Statistics (ONS) Open Geography Portal.
